## PyPod

Python console music player

### Installation

```bash
$ pip install python-pod
```


### Usage
```bash
$ pypod <path-to-directory>
$ pypod filename.wav
```

### Development

```bash
$ brew install portaudio
$ poetry install --with dev
```

